# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#  🔐 GRIDZBOTZ — Environment Secrets
#
#  Setup:
#    1. cp .env.example .env
#    2. Fill in your REAL keys below
#    3. source .env  (or add to your shell profile)
#    4. NEVER commit .env to git (.gitignore already excludes it)
#
#  How it works:
#    TOML configs contain safe placeholders/defaults.
#    resolve_secrets() in src/config/secrets.rs reads these env vars
#    and overrides the config values at startup.
#    If an env var is not set, the TOML value is used as-is.
#
#  Key rotation:
#    1. Generate new key at provider portal
#    2. Update this .env file
#    3. Restart bot — no code/config changes needed
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ─── REQUIRED: RPC Endpoint ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Primary Solana RPC (Chainstack, QuickNode, Helius, etc.)
# Get yours at: https://chainstack.com or https://quicknode.com
GRIDZBOTZ_RPC_URL=https://solana-mainnet.core.chainstack.com/YOUR_KEY_HERE

# ─── OPTIONAL: Fallback RPC ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Auto-failover if primary >150ms or fails
# GRIDZBOTZ_FALLBACK_RPC_URL=https://YOUR-QUICKNODE-ENDPOINT.quiknode.pro/YOUR_KEY/

# ─── REQUIRED: Jupiter API Key ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# Get free at: https://portal.jup.ag
GRIDZBOTZ_JUPITER_API_KEY=your-jupiter-api-key-here

# ─── REQUIRED: Wallet Path ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Absolute path to your Solana keypair JSON
# Verify permissions: chmod 600 /path/to/id.json
GRIDZBOTZ_WALLET_PATH=/Users/j-mc/.config/solana/id.json

# ─── OPTIONAL: Jito MEV Protection ─────────────────────────────────────────
# Enable when scaling above $500 capital
# GRIDZBOTZ_JITO_TIP_LAMPORTS=100000

# ─── OPTIONAL: Logging ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
RUST_LOG=info
# For debugging: RUST_LOG=debug
# For tracing:   RUST_LOG=trace
